{"tid":681694,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[反朗陣營] 賤種朗 逃稅6月15日判刑 念力集氣坐監區","createTime":"2018-05-28T09:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T07:28:09.000Z","uid":54373,"like":23,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"44a8df078a57a6b183ad81382729ac067dcdf89b","tid":681694,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nUPDATE 2018.5.28<br />\n賤種朗 逃稅1470萬<br />\n<br />\n想用1400萬歐元求繞,唔洗坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢類案應該都唔使坐,但柒頭逃稅金額龐大,個官點判好難講<br />\n而且第一庭唔認罪,所以一定要判佢具阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤種咪用美斯比<br />\n美斯逃稅470萬,而且係認罪<br />\nC朗係1470萬,仲要唔認罪,但第2堂佢大律師大敗,無得救"},{"pid":"8c1442a27ddd1d28e9438cfb32818e27396b8ba3","tid":681694,"uid":65743,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/170536_e4c923d0d5eaab4fa1fa43ba61b12d69.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F170536_e4c923d0d5eaab4fa1fa43ba61b12d69.gif&h=36a39884&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/170538_035bb78d8271a39e5574f3cf8689ae25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F170538_035bb78d8271a39e5574f3cf8689ae25.gif&h=0a8f9d0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffada2ac6e43f132a69d4a6dad6fa6734b0ca7eb","tid":681694,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"賤種咪用美斯作比較<br />\n<br />\n金額就算唔講<br />\n係認罪 同 唔認罪 既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse